50|$|Payment of {{less tax}} {{is the driving}} force behind most '{{offshore}}' activity. Due to the use of offshore centers, investors are able to conduct investment activities in a more profitable fashion. Often, taxes levied by an investor's home country are critical to the profitability of any given investment. Using offshore-domiciled special purpose mechanisms (or vehicles) an investor may reduce the <b>amount</b> <b>of</b> <b>tax</b> <b>payable,</b> allowing the investor to achieve greater profitability overall.|$|E
